name: pyls-black
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyls-black" %}
{% set version = "0.4.6" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 33700e5ed605636ea7ba39188a1362d2f8602f7301f8f2b8544773886f965663

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - black
    - python-language-server
    - toml

test:
  imports:
    - pyls_black
    - pyls_black.plugin

about:
  home: https://github.com/rupert/pyls-black
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Black plugin for the Python Language Server'
  dev_url: https://github.com/rupert/pyls-black

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - andfoy
    - ccordoba12
    - steff456
